Package com.example.napkinapp.models

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.napkinapp.models.Event
public class Event extends Object
Model class of an Event. it contains all raw the data of an event as well as lists of users (androidId) that are waitlisted, chosen, cancelled, and registered in this event.
